    <title>Response to President Obama&#039;s American Jobs Act</title>
    <link>http://www.newamerica.net/publications/policy/response_to_president_obamas_american_jobs_act</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-date field-field-pubdate&quot;&gt;
